text: Cozy and welcoming 2 bedroom 1 bath wood and stone Chalet-style home on over an acre in Maple Falls. The home features wood floors, vaulted ceilings, an updated kitchen and an extra room for entertaining upstairs. With over an acre of property, including a fenced yard, shop space and additional outbuildings, theres room for all your hobbies. The 2 bay garage has a bonus room as well. Enjoy views of the foothills plus proximity to Mount Baker and the great outdoors. This turn-key home is ready for it's next owner!

FANTASTIC INVESTOR OPPORTUNITY!Open floor-plan with spacious rooms and ample storage throughout. Potential for a 4th bedroom on the lower level, plus an extra unfinished area for added flexibility. Amazing potential with this rare gem! Dont miss out on all the fantastic Sudden Valley amenities!

Tucked away in a quiet neighborhood, this charming 3-bedroom, 1.75-bath home offers privacy and comfort. The large backyard, bordered by a serene forest, and a deck off the dining room, provide peaceful outdoor space. Inside, the open-concept layout fills the home with natural light, creating an inviting atmosphere perfect for entertaining. Enjoy recent updates including new paint, solid-core interior doors, modern fixtures, white shaker cabinetry, quartz countertops, new carpet, and LVP flooring. Featuring gas and wood burning fireplaces for added warmth. The spacious primary bedroom features an ensuite bath. Just minutes to downtown shopping and dining, this home combines seclusion with convenience. Dont miss out on this lovely retreat!

This one of a kind 1966 home in Lynden is one you won't want to miss! Located on a corner lot with an attached garage and carport with room for RV storage within walking distance to downtown Lynden. The main floor hosts 2 bedrooms and 1 full bath, a sizeable laundry room along with the open concept living/dining/kitchen space. In the partially finished basement you add a bedroom, bathroom, large rec room along with a second kitchen with a vintage oven! This home boasts so much character with HUGE potential. Call today if interested!

RARE double-parcel private estate in the heart of Bellingham just minutes to shopping, Downtown, and I-5. Pacific Northwest JEWEL on expansive half-acre, park-like, DOUBLE LOT in the heart of Bellingham. Architected landscaping elevates outdoor entertaining. Attention to detail and craftsmanship shows in inlaid hardwood floors and the custom cherry kitchen. Formal Living, Dining, and private office spaces exude elegance with curved walls of windows. Enjoy stunning sunsets over the City and Bellingham Bay from the Great Room and expansive west-facing deck. Zero-step entry and a main-level primary suite ensures ease of living. Stay active in the well-equipped home gym. Trailhead across the street offers endless outdoor exploration.

Welcome to Hannah Creek! This neighborhood in Bellingham is right next to miles of hiking and biking trails on Galbraith Mountain. Enter to see the spacious living room and open kitchen with a big island. A deck looks over the backyard and greenbelt with a small creek. Upstairs has a spacious primary bedroom, and 2 other bedrooms plus a convenient utility room. Downstairs is a spacious rec room and a roughed in bathroom, with access to the patio and fully fenced backyard, perfect for your dog. The home has cozy radiant floor heat throughout, with different temperature zones you can control. You can be hiking trails, or downtown, in 10 minutes! New roof in 2023. Don't miss this one!

Spacious well maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is situated on a huge flat double lot on corner with a secluded picnic and fire pit area to enjoy along with other outdoor fun, plus there's 3 outbuildings and firewood ready for the 2 fireplaces inside too. Features inside include large living room with beautiful fireplace and lots of natural light. The kitchen has an abundance of cupboards and opens to the dining area with a newer wood stove to dine by. There's lots of room in a 2nd living space in the family room off dining/kitchen area. King size master bedroom includes ensuite bathroom complete with soaking tub, separate shower and walk-in closet. An enclosed entry porch and a bigger enclosed deck in back are more spots to relax.

This exquisitely cared-for Geneva Neighborhood 2-story home features a graceful design & spacious layout. Enter the expansive living room, where vaulted ceilings & over-height windows w/plantation shutters & drapes create an elegant atmosphere. The open-concept dining area & gourmet kitchen are perfect for entertaining. Primary suite w/remodeled bath & walk-in are on the main floor, along w/ laundry & a powder room. Upstairs, are 2 large guest BR's, a large Bonus Room w/closet & remodeled 3/4 bath. The back deck & covered entertaining area are magazine-cover worthy, leaving the rest of the large, fenced back yard for gardening, games & gatherings! Extras include an instant-on backup generator, a large 2-car garage + a garden shed!

The opportunity you've been waiting for is here! Build your dream home on this water view property nestled within the Horizon community near Semiahmoo resort & country club. Have the best of both worlds by creating a home tailored to your needs while enjoying your peaceful living spaces within a vibrant community. This privately gated neighborhood includes walking trails, Boche ball courts, horseshoe pits w/ a future park coming soon. Bring your own plans, create your own plans, or bring your own builder to make this piece of property come to life & design your forever home. Dont have a builder? No problem, as Noffke Homes can offer assistance in building your custom home upon request.

Welcome to your new home - Mid county location, one level, and full of light! This 3 bdrm, 1.75 bath home has a great floor plan, kitchen with large counter island & eating bar. You will love the cozy gas FP in Family Room off of 2 car garage and easy access to patio in back yard. Roof is newer, less than 5 years old. It is private, on a large corner lot and partially fenced with storage sheds for your extra things. Perfect home waiting for your dcor.

Welcome home to this well-maintained Sandy Point Heights rambler. Move-in ready with fresh exterior paint, an open floor plan, and vaulted ceilings. Spacious kitchen comes with ample storage and space to cook & bake. Relax in a fully fenced, level backyard with an automatic gate, extensive parking space for RVs, boats, or multiple vehicles. Plus a versatile 36x24 shop featuring dual 9ft high automatic doors, a storage loft, and a lean-to for additional covered storage. Enjoy front and back decks for outdoor living. Views of Mt Baker & Lummi Bay views as well. Short distance to the community amenities: seasonal pool and golf course, marina with a boat launch, tennis courts, clubhouse, and more.

This spacious 4-bed, 2-bath home is situated on almost a half-acre lot in the desirable Happy Valley neighborhood on the Southside of Bellingham. Just a stones throw from Joes Garden and Western Washington University, this property offers convenience and potential. The home features a fully fenced backyard and paid off solar panels(36-LG ACe 375-watt) black-framed modules worth over $32, 000, installed in 2021. With all living spaces on one level, its ideal for a variety of lifestyles. Investor alertthis property is being sold as-is, offering a fantastic opportunity to renovate or customize to your liking. According to City of Bellingham, 2 ADUs (either attached or detached) could be added. Prime location with endless possibilities!

Discover the brand-new 2-story floor plan at The Ridge in Blaine, offered for the first time! This home boasts a primary bedroom on the main floor for easy living and convenience. With 4 bedrooms in total, one can be used as a home office on the main level. The second story offers a versatile bonus loft area. Designed with comfort and style, this home includes luxury vinyl plank flooring, quartz countertops, and modern finishes throughout. The open & bright floorplan and flexible layout make this home perfect for any lifestyle. Conveniently located near downtown Blaine and I-5 for easy access to all amenities. $5, 000 Buyer Credit available with our preferred lender, Becky Farrar at Evergreen Home Loans. Don't miss this amazing opportunity!

This is a gem of an investment property right in the heart of Fairhaven in the Urban Village! Live in the main 3 bed house and get a great interest rate, and then rent the two upper 2 bedroom units. All the character is intact with crown molding, white shaker cabinets, built-ins and each room is very generously sized. The upper 2 units have access from an exterior stairway off the back side of the triplex. There is a basement that has a work shop and storage units, along with coin-op washer and dryer (for the upper units, but they are W/D ready, too) and a 3/4 bath that is about .75% done, and additional units could be added down there. Electrical, plumbing, furnaces and hot water were updated in 2000 or sooner.

Welcome to your dream home at 604 North Forest Court! This 4-bedroom, 2.25-bathroom residence is a perfect blend of comfort and style. Step inside to a cozy and inviting atmosphere, with fresh new carpet throughout. The home boasts brand-new siding and windows, ensuring energy efficiency and a modern look. The kitchen features newer appliances, plenty of storage and counter-space! The primary bedroom includes a huge closet and a walk-in tile shower. Head downstairs to a fully finished basement featuring a large family room, 2 bedrooms and a bathroom providing ample space for entertainment or relaxation. Park-like private back yard with mature trees and large deck is perfect for entertaining.

Welcome to this beautifully maintained 3BD, 2BA rambler boasts 1, 477 square feet of inviting living space, perfect for entertaining. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow, enhanced by easy care vinyl plank floors and slate entry. Enjoy cooking in the modern kitchen featuring maple cabinetry and granite countertops. The cozy fireplace in the living area adds warmth and ambiance, while the air conditioning ensures comfort year round. The attached 2 car garage with plenty of storage. Step outside to your private oasis to unwind on the expansive deck that overlooks a serene greenbelt. The .14-acre lot offers a tranquil setting. The Sudden Valley Community offers parks, trails, swimming pool, beaches, marina, golf, and restaurants.

This is a rare opportunity to own a charming two-bedroom, one-bath cottage with beach rights on the west side. A bright open-concept floor plan featuring a wood fireplace in the heart of the cottage, and an updated kitchen that opens onto a large deck. The covered front porch looks over a beautifully landscaped pond, a sun-drenched private yard that is perfect for entertaining, and two sheds for beach toys. Privately owned beach with front-row seats for stunning sunsets and whale watching. Only 30 minutes from Vancouver, the perfect vacation oasis. Don't miss out on this great opportunity to have a piece of paradise close to the sea!

Bay Rim Condominiums is in the heart of Birch Bay! One of the best situated condos in the complex, just steps from the refreshing heated pool! Completely remodeled, 2 Bedroom/1.5 Baths. Kitchen w/quartz counter-tops, tile back-splash & plenty of counter/cupboard-space. New flooring, lighting & carpet w/quartz in both bathrooms! Community boasts private-beach w/gated access where low-tides bring hours of beachcombing & tons of sea-life to explore. Walk for miles, bike trails along the waterfront, area provides activities galore! Make this your primary residence, 2nd home or rental property.. this is just it!

This beautiful 3300 square foot 4 bedroom / 4 bathroom Ferndale home has plenty of room for everyone . Featuring a vaulted main floor entry, two living rooms and a den / office / library, and a large bright and cheery kitchen with a walk in pantry. The primary bedroom boasts a french door entrance with two spacious walk-in closets. Enjoy your morning coffee on the peaceful, spacious front deck or a BBQ gathering on the back deck. The back yard is fully fenced and has a shed that can house all your big tools and yard equipment. The seller has recently installed a new heat pump A/C unit and an EV charger in the garage.

Step into this beautifully designed 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath craftsman-style home and experience the perfect blend of classic charm and contemporary living. From the inviting front porch to the vaulted ceilings, every detail is crafted for comfort and style. The spacious living room is ideal for entertaining, while the modern kitchen, featuring sleek countertops and high-end appliances, makes meal preparation a breeze. Upstairs, the generously sized bedrooms provide a peaceful retreat, and the master suite includes a luxurious en-suite bath. Outdoor lovers will appreciate the private deck and patio - perfect for morning coffee or weekend barbecues. With its thoughtful design and abundant natural light, this home is a true gem.

Woods Point is a gated and active adult community for those 55 and older, featuring amenities like a community lodge, pickle ball court, and walking trail. This Landed Gentry home offers main-level living with vaulted ceilings in the spacious great room, and includes a primary bedroom, a second bedroom, bathroom and laundry all on the main floor. The second level has a third bedroom and full bathroom. Enjoy the 260 sq ft covered patio with a gas fireplace overlooking a fully enclosed fenced back yard with an irrigation system maintained by the HOA. The home features designer finishes soft close cabinet drawers, quartz counters and beautiful tile details, plus a finished two-car garage.

Turn key buildable lot in the coveted and private gated community of Mt Baker Rim in Glacier. Beautiful parcel with septic system already installed. Quiet culdesac location and the last lot in the Rim that has a view of Mt Baker. Low annual dues include clubhouse, outdoor seasonal pool, tennis courts, gated entrance, garbage and recycling. Easy access to Mt. Baker Ski Area, hiking, mountain biking, river rafting and fishing. Bring your plans and your builder and create your mountain dream home.

Affordable living in a central location, just steps to Birch Bay and minutes to I5 and Lynden. Adorable 2 bed and 1 bath home on a massive nearly quarter acre lot! Gourmet kitchen, dining, and living room areas. Recently installed mini-split system for heating and cooling! Your own private backyard oasis that is fully fenced, an oversized deck, and two storage sheds. Large driveway for tons of off-street parking and room to park your toys. RV hookups! Ask about a $5, 000 credit to buyer!

This fully remodeled and upgraded top floor condo is now on the market! The new remodel offers 3bd/2ba, 1234 sq/ft, a beautiful kitchen, SS appliances, under cabinet lighting, hard surface counters, new trim and flooring, a/c, vaulted ceilings, beautiful fire place, heated bathroom floors and so much more. Private primary suite with floor to ceiling tile shower and full glass shower door, dual vanity and walk in closet. This condo includes a garage for covered parking and/or storage space. Located in a great location with lots of great amenities nearby including spa, gym, pool and steak house. This is a 55+ community, but buyers can be between 41-55 with rental possibilities.

Step into a rare opportunity to own a cozy 2-bed, 1-bath home nestled on an expansive 8, 000+ sqft lot. Built in 2014, this thoughtfully maintained single-wide features brand-new carpet & fresh paint, offering a move-in-ready canvas for your personal touch. Surrounded by tall cedars, the property boasts serene, park-like feel. The generous backyard invites gardening enthusiasts to cultivate farm to table living, while the west end of the lot provides an ideal space to add a shop or ADU w/electric already plumbed. Enjoy the benefits of land ownership with no space rent, all while being conveniently located just minutes from I-5 & Ferndale's amenities. This is your chance to own a home & build equity at a cost more affordable than market rent.

Tucked away in quiet corner of peaceful neighborhood, this 3 bed, 2 bath Smart Home door bell, lock and thermostat, rambler is perfectly move-in ready! Cherry hardwood floors, new carpet and all blackout blinds! Stainless appliances, gas range and granite counters in open kitchen with instahot, cabinet storage galore, under mount lights, extra outlets and big pantry! Huge primary suit with large walk-in closet, double sinks and storage! New AC and furnace with Reme Halo whole home air purifier. Enjoy open living, bonus and dining space with slider to private deck, plumbed for gas BBQ and fully fenced yard. Adjacent to walking trails and green space; woods and wildlife! This well-kept home has large 2-car garage, front-load washer and dryer!
nearby_schools: Northwest Educational Service District 189, Bellingham Public Schools

text: Tucked away at the end of a quiet cul de sac, fantastic location walking distance to Barkley Village! Fully updated and lives like new, this 4 bedroom townhome will not disappoint! Open concept living on the main floor with 4 bedrooms upstairs including a primary suite with a private balcony. Everything inside is brand new including LVP flooring and carpet, doors and trim, white shaker cabinetry, quartz countertops, stainless appliances, LED lighting, and fresh paint. Oversized 2 car garage with brand new garage door and this home abuts the famous Bellingham interurban trail system!
